<p>
The course teaches how to design and implement efficient tools,
protocols and systems in a distributed environment.
The course gives some hands-on experience as well as some
theoretical background.
The programming assignments and the project in the course should be done in C / C++ with 
some exceptions. User interface parts of programs can be built in java if that is desired.
The assignments will  be evaluated on the Ugrad11-Ugrad20 cluster in the
undergrad lab.
</p>
For more information about the course please contact the instructor. 

